# ----------------------------------------------------------------------

# Node.js, npm, and yarn.

node_modules
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*


# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# | macOS                                                              |
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------

._*
.AppleDouble
.DS_Store
.localized
.LSOverride
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes


# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
